Description:
Quality without Compromise
Quality meets style in this impressive single-level family home, with its combination render and exposed brick frontage. Immaculately maintained, the property has four good-sized bedrooms, with the master zoned to the front and a walk-in robe and pristine ensuite with shower and double basins. The other three bedrooms share a bathroom with separate bath and shower.
The open-plan kitchen is a dream to use, with its stone bench tops, breakfast bar, gas cooking, dishwasher and storage space everywhere you look. The living/dining area is spacious and light-filled and made super-comfortable by a big split system. And just when you thought it couldn't get much better, there's a huge formal lounge with windows overlooking the front garden.
Flooring in the bedrooms is bliss-for-your-feet carpet, and elsewhere is fabulous easy-care gleaming cream tiling. Ducted heating provides warmth when in need.
A double remote garage keeps your cars safe and sound - and because this property gem is located just minutes from Parkmore Shopping Centre and the Hub at Dandenong - shopping is a breeze. Surrounded by verdant parklands with multiple walking tracks, this home is uniquely positioned and perfectly styled for quality family living.

Description:
Young, Modern and Affordable!
Quality meets affordability in this impressive, low maintenance family home positioned in the popular Metro Village Dandenong. A fine first home, a strong investment or a perfect downsize. Spacious living and outdoor entertaining areas are complimented by 3 spacious bedrooms and 2 bathrooms.
There is plenty to love about this home with it's modern fully tiled kitchen with ample bench tops with stainless steel appliances including dishwasher, rangehood and underbench wall oven. Both the adjoining fully tiled dining room plus the spacious carpeted living area both offer sliding glass door access to the north facing courtyard garden. All 3 bedrooms are carpeted with built in robes. The main bedroom serviced by a walk in robe and full ensuite bathroom. The family bathroom is well located between the two other bedrooms.
Enjoy all the extra features including remote control single car garage with internal access, split system heating & cooling and much more. Walking distance to the city centre and Dandenong station plus easy access to Monash & Eastlink plus bike and walking tracks.

Description:
2 Storey Stunner in Wonderful Locale!
Exuding style & comfort, this graceful 5-bedroom, double storey family home situated in a prime position is an opportunity not to miss.
Highlighted by a light-filled and spacious main living zone inclusive of a formal lounge with open fireplace, dining and family zone all strewn with quality polished wood flooring. An airy timber themed kitchen impressing with gas cook top, dishwasher and a walk through pantry to the tidy laundry.
Wander upstairs to encounter 2 expansive bedrooms with built-in robes and A/C along with a central bathroom with shower, dual vanity and a separate toilet. Perfect for a kids' retreat. The lower level is home to the remaining 3 bedrooms (2 with BIR), the enormous master bedroom is graced with a huge walk-in robe and ensuite, while the delightful shared bathroom has a separate shower to bath.
Opening out from the main living area is the versatile outdoor entertaining space: a generous iron bark deck enjoying a full function outdoor BBQ (gassed to house) and commercial basin. All of this overlooks the gorgeous garden with fish pond, green house, shed, and 2 x water tanks for toilet and garden.
Further features include, entrance foyer, ducted heating, carport with roller door to secure area, lengthy driveway for parking numerous vehicles and recently re stumped.
Ideally located only a stone's throw to, Princes Hwy, Gardiner Reserve, Dandenong Plaza and Dandenong Market, transport, hospital, Yarraman station, schools, EastLink and Monash Freeways.

Description:
Approved plans & permits for 5 townhouses!
Sitting on a total land area of 975 sqm this property is perfect for builders or developers who are immediately ready to start their next project. The endorsed plans and permit come together with: Full Engineering Drawings, Soil Report, Landscape Plan, Energy Reports, Land Surveyor Plan, South East Water Approvals and Preliminary Building Permit meaning that you would literally be ready to start the development immediately after the settlement. The approved plans are for the construction of 5 townhouses which have the following features:
Unit 1 – 171.62 sqm or 18.47 sqs – 3 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, double lock up garage (Street Facing)
Unit 2 – 171.13 sqm or 18.42 sqs – 3 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, double lock up garage
Unit 3 – 145.00 sqm or 15.61 sqs – 2 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, single carport
Unit 4 – 171.13 sqm or 18.42 sqs – 3 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, double lock up garage
Unit 5 – 171.62 sqm or 18.47 sqs – 3 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, double lock up garage (Street Facing)
Sitting in a highly sought after and central location that is minutes’ walk to Dandenong Plaza, Dandenong Market, Hospital and all other major amenities including public transport services and Dandenong’s CBD this property should appeal to any builder/developer who is wanting to take advantage of Dandenong’s continuous capital growth and potential.
With an existing weatherboard dwelling that features 3 bedrooms and is currently leased for $1304 per calendar month this property could also be a fantastic long term investment.
To view all of the plans and all relevant documentation as well as the property please contact Neb Delibasic on 0411 332 467.

Description:
Contemporary combined with Convenience!
LJ Hooker proudly presents this golden opportunity which is ideal for all first home buyers, downsizers and Astute investors looking to be nestled in a highly sought-after and central pocket of Dandenong. This well-maintained home is within a short distance to all amenities and provides the convenient and ideal lifestyle you have been searching for. To all the investors out there, this home is currently leased out to lovely tenants for $1390PCM on a month to month basis.
Offering 2 very good-sized bedrooms with BIR, master bedroom with access to the spacious balcony overlooking the lovely park and Dandenong Creek Trail, a spacious family area, second living zone, dining area adjacent to the delightful kitchen equipped with gas cooking and an abundance of cupboard space. The second balcony, main bathroom, separate toilet and laundry make up the interior of this lovely home.
Features of this home include: split system, electric wall heater, dishwasher, single lock-up garage and much more!
Located within a stones-throw away from Dandenong Station, Dandenong Plaza, Dandenong Market, multiple Pre-schools, Primary Schools and High Schools. Dandenong Bypass/Eastlink, Dandenong CBD, Dandenong Creek walking trail, public transport and recreational facilities. This home is all but ready for you to make it your own.
Do not miss out on this excellent opportunity!
Call Ben Jusufi or Burak Gul for any further information!
